{"tid":1380912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要］蓄聾狗衝，乜鳩都出呀！［中後排嘅同我入嚟］","createTime":"2019-07-29T06:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T00:41:58.000Z","uid":258521,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3be591145b1b154bff124c0f0a503d3830b8cf69","tid":1380912,"uid":258521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:27:29.000Z","msg":"蓄聾次次都係死衝過嚟，中後排就淆曬底 ，防線崩潰，玩完<br />\n<br />\n中後排嘅可唔可以唔好驚呀？<br />\n佢地又冇攞槍指住你<br />\n<br />\n你一驚，一走，前線就冇曬cover<br />\n等同任由啲蓄聾去打人去拉人<br />\n當前線愈來愈少人，你仲點抗爭落去？<br />\n<br />\n所以拜託大家睇清楚<br />\n當蓄聾狗衝過嚟嘅時候<br />\n後面啲黑驚就一定冇得用槍，佢地驚誤傷蓄聾<br />\n所以我哋面對嘅係&ldquo;手持木棍&rdquo;嘅蓄聾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">當蓄聾狗衝過嚟，中後排：<br />\n第一，唔好驚<br />\n第二，唔好跑<br />\n第三，唔好背對佢地<br />\n第四，見到有巴絲被攻，要幫拖救人<br />\n第五，前線叫退先慢退，唔好令到前線落單</span><br />\n<br />\n救得一個得一個呀！！<br />\n<br />\n中後排要識做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb7bd08677dab57a58db07734f6cf482dd25db8","tid":1380912,"uid":258521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"自推1000次"},{"pid":"8f2301023bfd873d5273dc7fb8d45658bb918a4b","tid":1380912,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:32:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［長文慎屌］727 728 賽後檢討<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380074</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"738efa89964fb38dbb70c25eb51c3ff355228e9d","tid":1380912,"uid":225272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:32:22.000Z","msg":"禁錯負皮sor"},{"pid"